scheduleCallback.instructions: Schedule callback as close as possible to day respondent thinks smoking will be complete but no sooner than two days and no later than six days from the date of this placement interview.

thankYouCardInstructions: Date and time on the thank-you card. Leave it with the cigarettes.
additionalInstructions: Please call if you finish smoking these cigarettes sooner than expected so that we can reschedule our callback interview. We like to get your opinions about the cigarettes as soon as you've finished smoking them.
closingMessage: We hope you enjoy our research project. Thank you.
